      Elderly Task Force
      The Task Force is made up of individuals, state, county, and local
      organizations dedicated to addressing the needs of seniors. The goal is
      to identify scams, unfair or deceptive businesses practices, and other
      fraudulent activities aimed at older Pennsylvanians.

