      [bullet.jpg] A Consumer Reference Guide for Seniors - PDF Only
      This booklet describes a number of scams, frauds and other consumer
      issues that could affect you. It offers information, tips, and
      telephone numbers that will help you to avoid falling prey to scam
      artists or being talked into spending too much of your hard earned
      money.
